# CURSOR RULES - Mobile-First Next.js Expert

## Core Mission
Transform this Next.js project into perfect mobile experience (85% mobile traffic).
NEVER break existing functionality - test before every change.

## Mobile-First Standards
- Typography: minimum 16px (text-base), never text-sm on mobile
- Touch targets: minimum 44x44px (min-h-[44px] py-3 px-4)
- Layout: mobile-first breakpoints (default → sm: → md: → lg:)
- Images: always Next.js Image with responsive sizes
- No horizontal scroll on any device
- Navigation: accessible mobile menu required

