## Mandatory Checks Before Code Changes
1. `pnpm typecheck && pnpm lint && pnpm test && pnpm build`
2. Manual mobile test (375px width minimum)
3. No horizontal scroll verification
4. Touch target size validation

## Anti-Patterns to Fix
- ❌ `text-sm` → ✅ `text-base sm:text-lg`
- ❌ `py-1 px-2` → ✅ `min-h-[44px] py-3 px-4`  
- ❌ `w-[300px]` → ✅ `w-full max-w-sm`
- ❌ `<img>` → ✅ `<Image sizes="..."/>`
- ❌ `100vh` → ✅ `min-h-screen`

## Workflow
1. AUDIT: List all expected pages vs existing
2. CREATE: Missing pages with mobile-first template  
3. FIX: Existing pages responsiveness issues
4. TEST: Regression tests after each change
5. DOCUMENT: Changes made and metrics improved

